item.title: CVE-2022-24802|2024-08-03T04:20:50.626Z -- rebeccastevens -- deepmerge-ts
item.description: deepmerge-ts is a typescript library providing functionality to deep merging of javascript objects. deepmerge-ts is vulnerable to Prototype Pollution via file deepmerge.ts, function defaultMergeRecords(). This issue has been patched in version 4.0.2. There are no known workarounds for this issue.
